  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/105449aae00f142add3ebe7024152d8c.avif?t=1734593560\" width=600 height=191 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Discover an Enchanting Adventure in the Forest of Middle Earth, Eleusis!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Eleusis, a mystical forest where souls gather as they await reincarnation. Become Kore, the girl of the forest, and embark on a journey to explore Eleusis and save it from the Black Rain.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◻ Explore a Magical Forest Freely</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the charm of an open world! Gather resources like flowers, trees, and animals, and uncover the secrets of the forest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/792cb255783f3173740f5cce9955f55b.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/792cb255783f3173740f5cce9955f55b.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/792cb255783f3173740f5cce9955f55b.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◻ The Battle Between Light and Darkness</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mama, the guardian of the forest, has collapsed, leaving Eleusis vulnerable to the spreading corruption of the Black Shadows. Join Kore and Porin on a journey to cleanse the forest and revive Mama.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/75cbc812ac73bde3d9ea3089c202768f.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/75cbc812ac73bde3d9ea3089c202768f.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/75cbc812ac73bde3d9ea3089c202768f.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◻ Adorable Companion Porin</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Porin isn’t just a cute friend but also the key to saving the forest’s destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/c862c7f62e5769d0b0e89ec558ecefa8.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/c862c7f62e5769d0b0e89ec558ecefa8.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/c862c7f62e5769d0b0e89ec558ecefa8.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/1762ae2b1dae1d834a059a29fb2edec7.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/1762ae2b1dae1d834a059a29fb2edec7.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/1762ae2b1dae1d834a059a29fb2edec7.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/dd653d8069b02d61e58cc3edd629dd7f.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/dd653d8069b02d61e58cc3edd629dd7f.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/dd653d8069b02d61e58cc3edd629dd7f.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◻ Mysterious Portals Powered by Light Stones</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Light Stones to activate portals scattered across the forest, enhancing your exploration with faster travel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/6ec6fb990b80de71f0a3014078a76a39.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/6ec6fb990b80de71f0a3014078a76a39.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/6ec6fb990b80de71f0a3014078a76a39.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◻ Customize Your Kore</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect various hairstyles and outfits to style Kore to your liking. Visit otherworldly merchants to further customize her appearance, including colors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/62eb87a61f83bcfe12484b4258cb316b.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/62eb87a61f83bcfe12484b4258cb316b.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/62eb87a61f83bcfe12484b4258cb316b.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◻ Generate Beautiful Characters in Real-Time</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using Stable Diffusion technology, collect souls with Kore to create new life. Witness the birth of beautiful and adorable girls resembling Kore in real-time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/da403b064f53948c0a403bd1d56f289c.poster.avif?t=1734593560\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/da403b064f53948c0a403bd1d56f289c.webm?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295290/extras/da403b064f53948c0a403bd1d56f289c.mp4?t=1734593560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◻ Recommended For</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      • Fans of cute characters and collecting beautiful girls</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Lovers of open-world exploration</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Players seeking a mix of relaxing gameplay and resource gathering </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Anyone who enjoys deep, story-driven single-player games  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Download now and become Kore, the Forest Courier, to change the destiny of Eleusis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a journey to protect the forest and restore its light!</p>",
